			</block>
            <view class="share-tips div" wx:if="{{activity.join_total == 0}}">
              <view class="name div">
                <text>赶快分享活动给大家</text>
              </view>
              <view class="tips div">
                <view class="div">
                  <text>方式一：点击右上角 "..." ，分享到群！</text>
                </view>
                <view class="div">
                  <text>方式二：点击下图“保存图片”，分享到朋友圈。</text>
                </view>
              </view>
              <view class="text-center div">
                <text>{{activity.title}}</text>
              </view>
              <view class="qr div">
                <image src="{{activity.code}}" bindtap="onPreviewImage" data-preview="{{activity.code}}" alt="" class="img-qr img"></image>
              </view>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
